'''''-ya''''' is a [[Quenya]] suffix of endearment.<ref>{{UT|15}}</ref> This may be the same as the possessive suffix [[-nya]] "my" as found in [[onya]] "my child" (from ''on-nya''), ''atya'' "my father", and ''amya'' "mother''.<ref>{{PE|17}}, p. 170</ref>
==Examples==
* '''Anardilya''' = "dear Anardil"<ref>{{UT|4}}</ref>
